name: Aggressive Growth
text:
Search your library for up to two basic land cards, reveal those cards, put one onto the battlefield tapped and the other into your hand, then shuffle.
If {u}{r} was spent to cast this spell, earthshake 2. (Distribute 2 +1/+1 counters among up to 2 target lands you control. You may have them become 0/0 Elemental creatures until end of turn. They're still lands.)
